text": " with that issue.", "tokens": [365, 300, 2734, 13], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.27494881369850854, "compression_ratio": 1.6940639269406392, "no_speech_prob": 1.1364010106262867e-06}, {"id": 50, "seek": 21188, "start": 220.44, "end": 223.72, "text": " At least not in the Vipassana tradition.", "tokens": [1711, 1935, 406, 294, 264, 691, 647, 640, 2095, 6994, 13], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.27494881369850854, "compression_ratio": 1.6940639269406392, "no_speech_prob": 1.1364010106262867e-06}, {"id": 51, "seek": 21188, "start": 223.72, "end": 227.4, "text": " Zen is maybe a little different story.", "tokens": [22387, 307, 1310, 257, 707, 819, 1657, 13], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.27494881369850854, "compression_ratio": 1.6940639269406392, "no_speech_prob": 1.1364010106262867e-06}, {"id": 52, "seek": 21188, "start": 227.4, "end": 232.88, "text": " There is a watershed between teachers that can lead you to enlightenment by teaching", "tokens": [821, 307, 257, 49728, 1296, 6023, 300, 393, 1477, 291, 281, 34661, 538, 4571], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.27494881369850854, "compression_ratio": 1.6940639269406392, "no_speech_prob": 1.1364010106262867e-06}, {"id": 53, "seek": 21188, "start": 232.88, "end": 237.4, "text": " you and teachers that can really deal with the issue of what happens if somebody does", "tokens": [291, 293, 6023, 300, 393, 534, 2028, 365, 264, 2734, 295, 437, 2314, 498, 2618, 775], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.27494881369850854, "compression_ratio": 1.6940639269406392, "no_speech_prob": 1.1364010106262867e-06}, {"id": 54, "seek": 21188, "start": 237.4, "end": 239.44, "text": " get enlightenment.", "tokens": [483, 34661, 13], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.27494881369850854, "compression_ratio": 1.6940639269406392, "no_speech_prob": 1.1364010106262867e-06}, {"id": 55, "seek": 23944, "start": 239.44, "end": 246.52, "text": " That's a whole other, from my perspective, that's a special skill.", "tokens": [663, 311, 257, 1379, 661, 11, 490, 452, 4585, 11, 300, 311, 257, 2121, 5389, 13], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.22111001828821694, "compression_ratio": 1.528301886792453, "no_speech_prob": 2.331505811525858e-06}, {"id": 56, "seek": 23944, "start": 246.52, "end": 251.56, "text": " Also to deal with what very occasionally happens.", "tokens": [2743, 281, 2028, 365, 437, 588, 16895, 2314, 13], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.22111001828821694, "compression_ratio": 1.528301886792453, "no_speech_prob": 2.331505811525858e-06}, {"id": 57, "seek": 23944, "start": 251.56, "end": 252.56, "text": " Doesn't happen often.", "tokens": [12955, 380, 1051, 2049, 13], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.22111001828821694, "compression_ratio": 1.528301886792453, "no_speech_prob": 2.331505811525858e-06}, {"id": 58, "seek": 23944, "start": 252.56, "end": 256.52, "text": " It's only happened a few times in my many decades career.", "tokens": [467, 311, 787, 2011, 257, 1326, 1413, 294, 452, 867, 7878, 3988, 13], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.22111001828821694, "compression_ratio": 1.528301886792453, "no_speech_prob": 2.331505811525858e-06}, {"id": 59, "seek": 23944, "start": 256.52, "end": 262.08, "text": " But there can sometimes be a thing where people get a sort of enlightenment experience that", "tokens": [583, 456, 393, 2171, 312, 257, 551, 689, 561, 483, 257, 1333, 295, 34661, 1752, 300], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.22111001828821694, "compression_ratio": 1.528301886792453, "no_speech_prob": 2.331505811525858e-06}, {"id": 60, "seek": 23944, "start": 262.08, "end": 268.12, "text": " has a mixture of pathology with it.", "tokens": [575, 257, 9925, 295, 3100, 1793, 365, 309, 13], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.22111001828821694, "compression_ratio": 1.528301886792453, "no_speech_prob": 2.331505811525858e-06}, {"id": 61, "seek": 26812, "start": 268.12, "end": 275.84000000000003, "text": " It's straddles enlightenment and a condition called DPDR, derealization depersonalization", "tokens": [467, 311, 1056, 345, 21915, 34661, 293, 257, 4188, 1219, 413, 17349, 49, 11, 15969, 304, 2144, 1367, 3953, 304, 2144], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.28034580115116003, "compression_ratio": 1.4310344827586208, "no_speech_prob": 1.0844667031051358e-06}, {"id": 62, "seek": 26812, "start": 275.84000000000003, "end": 277.72, "text": " disorder.", "tokens": [13399, 13], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.28034580115116003, "compression_ratio": 1.4310344827586208, "no_speech_prob": 1.0844667031051358e-06}, {"id": 63, "seek": 26812, "start": 277.72, "end": 284.0, "text": " This special class of teachers can deal with that issue too if it should come up.", "tokens": [639, 2121, 1508, 295, 6023, 393, 2028, 365, 300, 2734, 886, 498, 309, 820, 808, 493, 13], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.28034580115116003, "compression_ratio": 1.4310344827586208, "no_speech_prob": 1.0844667031051358e-06}, {"id": 64, "seek": 26812, "start": 284.0, "end": 291.0, "text": " So let's just call them masters for now for lack of any other term.", "tokens": [407, 718, 311, 445, 818, 552, 19294, 337, 586, 337, 5011, 295, 604, 661, 1433, 13], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.28034580115116003, "compression_ratio": 1.4310344827586208, "no_speech_prob": 1.0844667031051358e-06}, {"id": 65, "seek": 29100, "start": 291.0, "end": 299.6, "text": " Among masters there is a very, very, very special class of master.", "tokens": [16119, 19294, 456, 307, 257, 588, 11, 588, 11, 588, 2121, 1508, 295, 4505, 13], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.29615020751953125, "compression_ratio": 1.5093167701863355, "no_speech_prob": 2.2237263692659326e-06}, {"id": 66, "seek": 29100, "start": 299.6, "end": 301.56, "text": " That's a Buddha.", "tokens": [663, 311, 257, 16375, 13], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.29615020751953125, "compression_ratio": 1.5093167701863355, "no_speech_prob": 2.2237263692659326e-06}, {"id": 67, "seek": 29100, "start": 301.56, "end": 306.64, "text": " Because it was asked, well what's the difference between a Buddha and an arhat?", "tokens": [1436, 309, 390, 2351, 11, 731, 437, 311, 264, 2649, 1296, 257, 16375, 293, 364, 594, 15178, 30], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.29615020751953125, "compression_ratio": 1.5093167701863355, "no_speech_prob": 2.2237263692659326e-06}, {"id": 68, "seek": 29100, "start": 306.64, "end": 309.48, "text": " Arhat's fully enlightened, fully purified.", "tokens": [1587, 15178, 311, 4498, 36975, 11, 4498, 1864, 2587, 13], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.29615020751953125, "compression_ratio": 1.5093167701863355, "no_speech_prob": 2.2237263692659326e-06}, {"id": 69, "seek": 29100, "start": 309.48, "end": 314.88, "text": " What makes a certain arhat a Buddha?", "tokens": [708, 1669, 257, 1629, 594, 15178, 257, 16375, 30], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.29615020751953125, "compression_ratio": 1.5093167701863355, "no_speech_prob": 2.2237263692659326e-06}, {"id": 70, "seek": 31488, "start": 314.88, "end": 324.88, "text": " The answer is where there was no path, he discovered a path and made it available to", "tokens": [440, 1867, 307, 689, 456, 390, 572, 3100, 11, 415, 6941, 257, 3100, 293, 1027, 309, 2435, 281], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.271487311711387, "compression_ratio": 1.4733727810650887, "no_speech_prob": 1.2478860753617482e-06}, {"id": 71, "seek": 31488, "start": 324.88, "end": 326.6, "text": " the world.", "tokens": [264, 1002, 13], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.271487311711387, "compression_ratio": 1.4733727810650887, "no_speech_prob": 1.2478860753617482e-06}, {"id": 72, "seek": 31488, "start": 326.6, "end": 328.76, "text": " That's the traditional formulation.", "tokens": [663, 311, 264, 5164, 37642, 13], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.271487311711387, "compression_ratio": 1.4733727810650887, "no_speech_prob": 1.2478860753617482e-06}, {"id": 73, "seek": 31488, "start": 328.76, "end": 331.08, "text": " I'd modify that a little bit.", "tokens": [286, 1116, 16927, 300, 257, 707, 857, 13], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.271487311711387, "compression_ratio": 1.4733727810650887, "no_speech_prob": 1.2478860753617482e-06}, {"id": 74, "seek": 31488, "start": 331.08, "end": 343.8, "text": " I would say a single Buddha is a master who discovers something new and important about", "tokens": [286, 576, 584, 257, 2167, 16375, 307, 257, 4505, 567, 44522, 746, 777, 293, 1021, 466], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.271487311711387, "compression_ratio": 1.4733727810650887, "no_speech_prob": 1.2478860753617482e-06}, {"id": 75, "seek": 34380, "start": 343.8, "end": 345.08, "text": " enlightenment.", "tokens": [34661, 13], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.2515347344534738, "compression_ratio": 1.4350282485875707, "no_speech_prob": 3.0889486879459582e-06}, {"id": 76, "seek": 34380, "start": 345.08, "end": 354.92, "text": " As a result of that, there is widespread and profound positive change in the direction", "tokens": [1018, 257, 1874, 295, 300, 11, 456, 307, 22679, 293, 14382, 3353, 1319, 294, 264, 3513], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.2515347344534738, "compression_ratio": 1.4350282485875707, "no_speech_prob": 3.0889486879459582e-06}, {"id": 77, "seek": 34380, "start": 354.92, "end": 356.64, "text": " of human history.", "tokens": [295, 1952, 2503, 13], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.2515347344534738, "compression_ratio": 1.4350282485875707, "no_speech_prob": 3.0889486879459582e-06}, {"id": 78, "seek": 34380, "start": 356.64, "end": 361.48, "text": " Not just change the course of a few lives in a good way.", "tokens": [1726, 445, 1319, 264, 1164, 295, 257, 1326, 2909, 294, 257, 665, 636, 13], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.2515347344534738, "compression_ratio": 1.4350282485875707, "no_speech_prob": 3.0889486879459582e-06}, {"id": 79, "seek": 34380, "start": 361.48, "end": 362.48, "text": " That's a Buddha.", "tokens": [663, 311, 257, 16375, 13], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.2515347344534738, "compression_ratio": 1.4350282485875707, "no_speech_prob": 3.0889486879459582e-06}, {"id": 80, "seek": 34380, "start": 362.48, "end": 368.52, "text": " I'm not at all sure that the next Buddha will be one person.", "tokens": [286, 478, 406, 412, 439, 988, 300, 264, 958, 16375, 486, 312, 472, 954, 13], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.2515347344534738, "compression_ratio": 1.4350282485875707, "no_speech_prob": 3.0889486879459582e-06}, {"id": 81, "seek": 36852, "start": 368.52, "end": 375.4, "text": " The next Buddha may be a team, a team of enlightened scientists, for example.", "tokens": [440, 958, 16375, 815, 312, 257, 1469, 11, 257, 1469, 295, 36975, 7708, 11, 337, 1365, 13], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.24167376624213324, "compression_ratio": 1.5663716814159292, "no_speech_prob": 6.526344350277213e-06}, {"id": 82, "seek": 36852, "start": 375.4, "end": 380.79999999999995, "text": " If we think of Buddha as meaning discover something that has not been known in the past", "tokens": [759, 321, 519, 295, 16375, 382, 3620, 4411, 746, 300, 575, 406, 668, 2570, 294, 264, 1791], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.24167376624213324, "compression_ratio": 1.5663716814159292, "no_speech_prob": 6.526344350277213e-06}, {"id": 83, "seek": 36852, "start": 380.79999999999995, "end": 386.08, "text": " and that is deep enough and powerful enough to change the course of human history, that", "tokens": [293, 300, 307, 2452, 1547, 293, 4005, 1547, 281, 1319, 264, 1164, 295, 1952, 2503, 11, 300], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.24167376624213324, "compression_ratio": 1.5663716814159292, "no_speech_prob": 6.526344350277213e-06}, {"id": 84, "seek": 36852, "start": 386.08, "end": 389.03999999999996, "text": " might turn out to be a team effort.", "tokens": [1062, 1261, 484, 281, 312, 257, 1469, 4630, 13], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.24167376624213324, "compression_ratio": 1.5663716814159292, "no_speech_prob": 6.526344350277213e-06}, {"id": 85, "seek": 36852, "start": 389.03999999999996, "end": 392.79999999999995, "text": " Might, who can say?", "tokens": [23964, 11, 567, 393, 584, 30], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.24167376624213324, "compression_ratio": 1.5663716814159292, "no_speech_prob": 6.526344350277213e-06}, {"id": 86, "seek": 36852, "start": 392.79999999999995, "end": 397.76, "text": " This then gives us a map of total happiness.", "tokens": [639, 550, 2709, 505, 257, 4471, 295, 3217, 8324, 13], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.24167376624213324, "compression_ratio": 1.5663716814159292, "no_speech_prob": 6.526344350277213e-06}, {"id": 87, "seek": 39776, "start": 397.76, "end": 400.03999999999996, "text": " This is where we started.", "tokens": [639, 307, 689, 321, 1409, 13], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.26346224546432495, "compression_ratio": 1.823008849557522, "no_speech_prob": 2.0903482891299063e-06}, {"id": 88, "seek": 39776, "start": 400.03999999999996, "end": 405.48, "text": " Ordinary happiness for yourself.", "tokens": [29388, 4066, 8324, 337, 1803, 13], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.26346224546432495, "compression_ratio": 1.823008849557522, "no_speech_prob": 2.0903482891299063e-06}, {"id": 89, "seek": 39776, "start": 405.48, "end": 413.52, "text": " Then we talked about extraordinary happiness for yourself.", "tokens": [1396, 321, 2825, 466, 10581, 8324, 337, 1803, 13], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.26346224546432495, "compression_ratio": 1.823008849557522, "no_speech_prob": 2.0903482891299063e-06}, {"id": 90, "seek": 39776, "start": 413.52, "end": 425.12, "text": " Then we talked about how these lead to service to others, ordinary happiness for others,", "tokens": [1396, 321, 2825, 466, 577, 613, 1477, 281, 2643, 281, 2357, 11, 10547, 8324, 337, 2357, 11], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.26346224546432495, "compression_ratio": 1.823008849557522, "no_speech_prob": 2.0903482891299063e-06}, {"id": 91, "seek": 42512, "start": 425.12, "end": 428.84000000000003, "text": " and extraordinary happiness for others.", "tokens": [293, 10581, 8324, 337, 2357, 13], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.2895434432559543, "compression_ratio": 1.8780487804878048, "no_speech_prob": 1.6790472727734596e-06}, {"id": 92, "seek": 42512, "start": 428.84000000000003, "end": 432.64, "text": " Under extraordinary happiness for others, I mentioned teaching.", "tokens": [6974, 10581, 8324, 337, 2357, 11, 286, 2835, 4571, 13], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.2895434432559543, "compression_ratio": 1.8780487804878048, "no_speech_prob": 1.6790472727734596e-06}, {"id": 93, "seek": 42512, "start": 432.64, "end": 439.68, "text": " There's one other category and that is supporting teaching.", "tokens": [821, 311, 472, 661, 7719, 293, 300, 307, 7231, 4571, 13], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.2895434432559543, "compression_ratio": 1.8780487804878048, "no_speech_prob": 1.6790472727734596e-06}, {"id": 94, "seek": 42512, "start": 439.68, "end": 440.68, "text": " That's Dana, right?", "tokens": [663, 311, 23759, 11, 558, 30], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.2895434432559543, "compression_ratio": 1.8780487804878048, "no_speech_prob": 1.6790472727734596e-06}, {"id": 95, "seek": 42512, "start": 440.68, "end": 442.84000000000003, "text": " The Dana, the teacher Dana.", "tokens": [440, 23759, 11, 264, 5027, 23759, 13], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.2895434432559543, "compression_ratio": 1.8780487804878048, "no_speech_prob": 1.6790472727734596e-06}, {"id": 96, "seek": 42512, "start": 442.84000000000003, "end": 448.84000000000003, "text": " When you support teachers, you support their efforts to bring extraordinary happiness to", "tokens": [1133, 291, 1406, 6023, 11, 291, 1406, 641, 6484, 281, 1565, 10581, 8324, 281], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.2895434432559543, "compression_ratio": 1.8780487804878048, "no_speech_prob": 1.6790472727734596e-06}, {"id": 97, "seek": 42512,